{"tid":2000964,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好掛住以前細個同媽咪一齊去食元綠壽司既時間","createTime":"2020-05-04T07:55:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T08:24:43.000Z","uid":13160,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"418f1fc99c4db826e6f563b507e97c67b4cd4dc7","tid":2000964,"uid":13160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T07:55:12.000Z","msg":"個時細細個咩都唔識, <br />\n咩都唔洗擔心, 唔洗煩<br />\n同屋企人去到元綠壽司<br />\n聽住Twins既歌跟住唱<br />\n食咩壽司都加wasabi<br />\n再忍住唔喊<br />\n<br />\n依家大個都係忍住唔喊<br />\n最近媽咪好似口腔唔舒服<br />\n睇左3次醫生同急証都係未好<br />\n琴日聽到佢同啲兄弟姊妹講電話講到喊<br />\n又同我講要同我整聯名戶口<br />\n怕突然間有啲咩事<br />\n我叫佢唔好諗咁多, 無事既<br />\n之後佢又話佢開始記唔到野<br />\n佢成日擔心依樣果樣<br />\n即使瞓都係戴住口罩<br />\n搞到我都擔心埋一份`<br />\n<br />\n我想問下大家有無咩口腔專科介紹??"},{"pid":"a735a70d05473db05986d99b4c80d11d1324ba8b","tid":2000964,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T08:07:29.000Z","msg":"唔明喎，乜野口腔唔舒服，係咪蛀牙咋"},{"pid":"3322221e9bd57b949dd3972f92b3d49f15f9d06f","tid":2000964,"uid":202898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T08:08:34.000Z","msg":"不如睇牙醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4325744f7dec4fcea184669b7c5497f6d8ec3c09","tid":2000964,"uid":13160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a735a70d05473db05986d99b4c80d11d1324ba8b","tid":2000964,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T08:07:29.000Z","msg":"唔明喎，乜野口腔唔舒服，係咪蛀牙咋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T08:09:04.000Z","msg":"類似口腔生飛滋, 係喉嚨"},{"pid":"a3756a5020b38bdebbc3a89f9178083892dbcedd","tid":2000964,"uid":13160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3322221e9bd57b949dd3972f92b3d49f15f9d06f","tid":2000964,"uid":202898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T08:08:34.000Z","msg":"不如睇牙醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T08:11:19.000Z","msg":"有血喎, 佢話上顎痛添"},{"pid":"7ff6ca60b38064800c55dfce1971d4a315a4ee